</div>
 
<div>



<h2>Standard Life - Passive Plus III Pension Fund</h2>


<p>The fund aims to provide long term growth while being managed to a level of risk, rather than a level of return. This fund is risk level III and as such invests in both lower risk investments such as money market instruments and certain types of bonds, and higher risk investments such as equities and property. This may suit you if you have a balanced attitude to risk. The investments in the fund can be from around the world. The fund can also invest in absolute return funds that aim to provide positive investment returns regardless of the market.</p>
<div class="multi-document-download-container">
    

<a class="document-download-wrap pdf" href="/cdn/static/cms/documents/passive-plus-iii-pension-fund-june-2019.pdf">
