<h2>Standard Life - International Pension Fund</h2>


<p>The fund aims to provide long term growth and is designed for investors who are looking for exposure to global equity markets. The fund invests predominately in the shares of companies listed on the Global stock markets and is actively managed by Standard Life's investment team, who will select stocks to try to take advantage of opportunities they have identified.&nbsp;</p>
