<h2>Standard Life - iShares Index Linked Gilt Index Pension Fund</h2>


<p>The objective of the fund is to invest in UK Government Index-linked
securities (index-linked gilts) that have a maturity period of 5 years
or longer. It aims to achieve a return consistent to the FTSE UK Gilts
Index-Linked Over 5 Years Index, which is widely regarded as the
benchmark for UK pension fund investment in the longer dated end of the
UK index-linked gilt market.&nbsp;</p>
