<h2>Standard Life - BlackRock ACS World ex UK Equity Tracker Pension Fund</h2>


<p>The fund aims to invest in the shares of overseas companies (Europe,
Japan, Far East, US and Canadian markets) according to market
capitalisation weightings. Within each of those markets, the fund aims
to generate returns consistent with those of each country's primary
share market. This fund aims to achieve a return in line with the FTSE
All-World Developed ex-UK Index.&nbsp;</p>
